OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FLargely dry with sunny spells
OL,6,Fduring the morning. Cloud increasing
OL,7,Fto bring outbreaks of showery rain,
OL,8,Fperhaps locally heavy, by late
OL,9,Fafternoon. Feeling warm in sunshine.
OL,10,FBreezy.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FThe rain will clear eastwards
OL,13,Fduring the early evening with some
OL,14,Fbreaks developing in the cloudy and
OL,15,Fthe chance of an isolated shower.
OL,16,FWinds remain breezy.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
