OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FCloudy with showers, some of
OL,6,Fwhich could turn sharp at times,
OL,7,Fbefore easing during the afternoon as
OL,8,Fthe cloud breaks and turns more
OL,9,Fsettled overnight.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FDrier
OL,12,Fand sunnier with winds easing Sunday.
OL,13,FCloudier on Monday with isolated
OL,14,Fshowers in the east. Tuesday will be
OL,15,Fcloudy at times with showers and
OL,16,Ffreshening wind.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
